{
  "texts": [
    "In particular, the AI for EO (AI4EO) focuses on harnessing the power of Artificial Intelligence (i.e.",
    "promoting the implementation of ML and DL algorithms) with the vast amount of EO data now available.",
    "Similarly, Destination Earth, an initiative by the European Commission, aims to create a sophisticated AI-driven decision support system which will rely on a highly precise digital model of the Earth (i.e.",
    "digital twin Earth) to monitor and simulate both natural phenomena and human activity.",
    "The goal is to develop and evaluate scenarios that promote sustainable development and provide support for European environmental policies."
  ]
}